Dynamic Host Configuration Protocol

Apply floor



1 )
send DHCP discover to find DHCP servers

2 ) 
DHCP Server receives DHCP and Send a DHCP Offer

3 )
If DHCP Client get a few DHCP Offer pkts , and It will only handle the first DHCP Offer
And broad DHCP Request,including DHCP server and IP it uses

4 )
every DHCP will receive DHCP Request.If the DHCP server is itself
Send A DHCP ACK